# =============================================================================
# Docker Build Context Exclusions
# =============================================================================
# Files/directories listed here are NOT sent to Docker daemon during build
# This speeds up builds and prevents sensitive data leaks
#
# BEFORE USING:
# - Review each section and add/remove based on your project
# - Pay special attention to the SECRETS section
# - Add any project-specific files that shouldn't be in Docker images
# =============================================================================

